{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-322","title":"建筑物相关","sectionId":"chapter-14","sectionTitle":"人文历史需了解","pageStart":1571,"pageEnd":1575,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":6,"duplicateEntryCount":27,"pages":[{"number":1571,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"322 建筑物相关"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"landscape architecture园林建筑","headword":"landscape architecture"}]},{"number":1572,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"block of flats公寓楼","headword":"block of flats"}]},{"number":1573,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"small scale小规模","headword":"small scale"},{"type":"entry","text":"map out 在地图上标出；计划，安排","headword":"map out"},{"type":"entry","text":"lay the foundation 打地基","headword":"lay the foundation"}]},{"number":1574,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"spiral stair 旋转楼梯","headword":"spiral stair"}]},{"number":1575,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：They are planning to erect a seven-floor residential building.（他"},{"type":"text","text":"们计划要建一座七层的住宅楼。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：But is this place suitable? （但这个地点适合吗？）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I love your design of the balcony. （我喜欢你的阳台设计方"},{"type":"text","text":"案。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Thanks a lot. I'm glad that you love it. （谢谢。你能喜欢我很高"},{"type":"text","text":"兴。）"}]}]}